def largestRectangleArea(A):
    ans = 0
    A = [-1] + A
    A.append(-1)
    n = len(A)
    stack = [0]
    for i in range(n):
        while A[i] < A[stack[-1]]:
            h = A[stack.pop()]
            area = h*(i-stack[-1]-1)
            ans = max(ans, area)
        stack.append(i)
    return ans

from sys import stdin,stdout
def right(a,n):
    s=[]
    rs=[n]*n
    for i in range(n):
        while s!=[] and a[s[-1]]>a[i]:
            rs[s[-1]]=i
            s.pop()
        s.append(i)
    return rs
    
def left(a,n):
    s=[]
    ls=[-1]*n
    for i in range(n-1,-1,-1):
        while s!=[] and  a[s[-1]]>a[i]:
            ls[s[-1]]=i
            s.pop()
        s.append(i)
    return ls
    
for _ in range(int(stdin.readline())):
    n=int(stdin.readline())
    a=[int(x) for x in stdin.readline().split()]
    rs=right(a,n)
    ls=left(a,n)
    #print(ls,rs)
    m=0
    for i in range(n):
        m=max((rs[i]-ls[i]-1)*a[i],m)
    print(m)
